preliminary wells and has identified 150 additional well locations they would
like to develop.

<img src='http://www.gastar.com/images/operations/MAP-3-UPDATE.gif'</img>

http://www.gastar.com/globaloperations.cfm?pagesect=deepbossier

From their Web site:"...The Company drilled its first Glen Rose test, the
Wildman 6H in June 2010 and began drilling the second Glen Rose well, the
Wildman 8H, in November 2010. The Wildman 7H, its first horizontal Eagle Ford
well, was drilled in December 2010 and fracture stimulated in January 2011. If
exploration results are successful, the Company has identified approximately
150 additional well locations in the Glen Rose and Eagle Ford/Woodbine....".

